.Rhistory
*.RData
*.Rproj.user
.Rproj.user

# Data and output (large/generated files)
output
data
# GADM population CSVs — large build-only inputs for web/scripts/build_population.mjs,
# which turns them into the per-country web/public/data/pop/<CC>.json shards the
# clustering app ships. Keep the script + generated shards, not these source CSVs.
/gadm*_population.csv

